[Pakistan is another country that is suffering from a measles upsurge. Approximately 41 countries have already put off in 2020, or may put off in 2021, their measles campaigns due to the COVID-19 pandemic. This is leading to public health disasters for children, and a threat to the global health. - Mod.LK

